    Class Description
    Complex
    Class for complex numbers the complex numbers have the form a+bi (example 3+4i), where i is the square of the -1 and the base of the imaginary numbers the parts of a complex number are a= the real part b= the imaginary part with a camplex number you can calculate diferents operations.
    Fraction
    Represents a fraction Represents and resolve fractions
    Matrix
    Class to represent and manipulate matrix The function of this class is representing and manipulated matrix made of real numbers The class have calculation of basic functions in MxN matrix
